<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 15:12:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>梅洛尼誓言“重启”意大利与中国的合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周日誓言要“重启”与中国的合作，并在上任以来首次正式访问北京期间签署了一项三年行动计划。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国曲解南海协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</link><description>一名中国官员表示，中国海警在执行任务前接到通知，并在“现场确认”后放行了一艘船只。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:29:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国升级驻日军事指挥权，警告中国威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</link><description>美国周日宣布计划对其驻日军事指挥部进行重大调整，以加深与其盟友部队的协调，两国将中国视为该地区面临的“最大战略挑战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 03:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜在朝鲜战争周年纪念日发誓“彻底消灭”敌人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</link><description>据官方媒体朝中社周日报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩下令，誓言一旦发生战争，将“彻底摧毁”敌人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言要建立比特币“储备”，并援引中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-cites-china-competition-vowing-create-bitcoin-stockpile-2024-07-27/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普在周六的比特币会议上表示，美国必须主导该行业，否则中国就会主导该行业，这是他向加密货币倡导者发起的最新举动，北京方面已限制加密货币，他曾将其斥为“骗局”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 23:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-cites-china-competition-vowing-create-bitcoin-stockpile-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯与王讨论台湾和中国对俄罗斯的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周六会见中国外长王毅时，重申了华盛顿对北京对台湾行动的担忧以及对俄罗斯乌克兰战争的支持。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:37:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”迫使中国东北地区疏散、工厂停工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</link><description>据官方新华社周六报道，由于台风“盖美”带来大雨，中国东北地区有超过 27,000 人被疏散，数百家工厂被勒令停产。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾完成与北京达成协议以来首次南海补给任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</link><description>菲律宾外交部表示，周六，菲律宾在有争议的南海浅滩顺利完成了向其部队进行的补给行动，这是与中国达成的旨在缓和紧张局势的新安排下的首次此类任务。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 05:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯谴责北京在海上“升级行动”，并对台湾表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-wong-presses-myanmar-generals-change-tack-ahead-laos-summits-2024-07-27/</link><description>布林肯点名批评中国海岸警卫队在南海对菲律宾采取的敌对行动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-wong-presses-myanmar-generals-change-tack-ahead-laos-summits-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>司法部要求法院驳回 TikTok 对打击法律的挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/usdoj-tells-court-reject-tiktok-challenge-crackdown-law-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国司法部认为，中国拥有的 TikTok 由于可以获取美国人的个人数据而构成威胁，并声称中国可以操纵美国人通过 TikTok 消费的信息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/usdoj-tells-court-reject-tiktok-challenge-crackdown-law-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长就美国部署导弹向菲律宾发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-foreign-minister-warns-philippines-over-us-missile-deployment-2024-07-27/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅就美国部署中程导弹向菲律宾发出警告，称此举可能加剧地区紧张局势并引发军备竞赛。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 04:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-foreign-minister-warns-philippines-over-us-missile-deployment-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管经济步履蹒跚，但6月份中国工业利润仍实现较快增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-post-faster-gains-june-despite-faltering-economy-2024-07-27/</link><description>周六的官方数据显示，尽管企业正努力应对经济复苏不稳定、消费者信心下降的问题，但中国六月份工业利润增长较快。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 02:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profits-post-faster-gains-june-despite-faltering-economy-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦：新兴市场对中国工厂产能过剩表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</link><description>美国财长耶伦周五表示，包括一些G20国家在内的新兴市场与她一样对中国工业产能过剩感到担忧，并应敦促北京改变其经济模式。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>上海推出138亿美元基金支持集成电路、生物医药、人工智能等领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国商业中心上海周五宣布提供 1000 亿元人民币（137.9 亿美元）的资金，以促进其集成电路、生物医药和人工智能 (AI) 产业的发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 与中国外长王毅会面后，其办公室周五表示，英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军队。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>